---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Luke, Full-Stack Developer">
    <div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen">
        <Navbar />
        <main class="flex-grow bg-blue-200 py-8 sm:py-16 overflow-y-auto border-y-4 border-black">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-4 sm:p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
                    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-black mb-4 sm:mb-8 transform -rotate-1 break-words">About Luke</h1>

                    <div class="space-y-6 text-lg sm:text-xl text-black">
                        <p class="bg-blue-100 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] inline-block transform rotate-1">
                            Full-stack developer with 10 years of experience, specializing in crafting robust web applications. Based in Wroc≈Çaw, Poland.
                        </p>

                        <p>
                            As a seasoned developer, I've honed my skills in creating scalable, user-friendly solutions that drive business growth. My expertise spans from backend architecture to frontend design, ensuring seamless, end-to-end application development.
                        </p>

                        <p>
                            My journey in tech began with a curiosity about how things work, which naturally led me to coding. Today, I tackle complex problems with enthusiasm, turning them into elegant, efficient applications.
                        </p>

                        <p>
                            Beyond coding, I'm a proud husband and father to a wonderful son. Our family, complete with a cat and a dog, keeps me grounded and inspired. We love exploring the beautiful landscapes of Poland together.
                        </p>

                        <p>
                            In my free time, I embrace my inner geek. I'm an avid gamer, always ready for the next big release or a nostalgic replay of classics. This passion for games often influences my approach to creating engaging user experiences in my work.
                        </p>

                        <p>
                            I'm committed to continuous learning and sharing knowledge. You'll often find me experimenting with new technologies, contributing to open-source projects, or writing tech blogs to help fellow developers.
                        </p>

                        <p class="bg-blue-100 p-4 border-4 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] inline-block transform -rotate-1">
                            Whether it's developing a cutting-edge application or spending quality time with my family, I approach life with enthusiasm and a dedication to excellence.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
        <Footer />
    </div>
</Layout>